    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890650/extras/1f34b13b6b59fa1b43eee93113fc7124.poster.avif?t=1751667485\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890650/extras/1f34b13b6b59fa1b43eee93113fc7124.webm?t=1751667485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890650/extras/1f34b13b6b59fa1b43eee93113fc7124.mp4?t=1751667485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890650/extras/7f5292f7767d89e5143a4ac53f360bbb.webp?t=1751667485\" width=615 height=37 /></span><br>超过 30 座独特的塔楼可供建造和计数！发现他们的特殊能力并升级他们以获得最大的伤害！每个商人都将很乐意向您展示他们的新的和令人兴奋的塔的特殊库存。或者用神秘的国际象棋冒险并以更少的价格获得随机塔。<br><br><strong>试试看：</strong><br>🟠<strong>雷霆之塔（一次使多个敌人通电）</strong><br>🔵 <strong>治疗塔（战斗时治愈你和你的朋友）</strong><br>🟠<strong>守护塔（生成一个会巡逻的盟友）</strong><br>🔵<strong>猛击塔（攻击力强但射程短）还有更多！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890650/extras/ea26134347e3c779baed2c12c1cb9c88.poster.avif?t=1751667485\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890650/extras/ea26134347e3c779baed2c12c1cb9c88.webm?t=1751667485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890650/extras/ea26134347e3c779baed2c12c1cb9c88.mp4?t=1751667485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890650/extras/7f5292f7767d89e5143a4ac53f360bbb.webp?t=1751667485\" width=615 height=37 /></span><br>在敌人攻击之前迅速开始收集资源！从没有工具和资源开始会很困难，但是制作正确的工具，你会发现一套全新的资源来切割、挖掘和收集。制作缺失的资源来升级你的塔楼并击败即将到来的怪物到达你的生命水晶。使用工作台帮助您快速进步。<br><br><strong>一些方便的工具：</strong><br>🟠<strong>石斧（砍树、砍、砍）</strong><br>🔵<strong>木棍（必须保卫那个水晶）</strong><br>🟠<strong>铁铲（diggity煤和粘土）</strong><br>🔵<strong>石镐（铁听到我来了）还有更多！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890650/extras/b48427737584e110862e7b7b5883fe12.poster.avif?t=1751667485\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890650/extras/b48427737584e110862e7b7b5883fe12.webm?t=1751667485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890650/extras/b48427737584e110862e7b7b5883fe12.mp4?t=1751667485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890650/extras/7f5292f7767d89e5143a4ac53f360bbb.webp?t=1751667485\" width=615 height=37 /></span><br>游戏中的每种工具和每种武器都有一个特殊的技能树，可以帮助您更轻松地保护您的水晶。在十多种具有独特功能的武器和盔甲中进行选择。通过击败波浪并从怪物那里收集经验值来获得技能点。<br><br><strong>选择：</strong><br>🟠<strong>清道夫（采集时给予20%的额外物品）</strong><br>🔵<strong>旋转攻击（推回你附近的敌人）</strong><br>🟠<strong>大箭筒（向目标射更多箭）</strong><br>🔵<strong>Keen Eye 2（60% 的机会找到额外的物品）还有更多！</strong>",
